modules.description: Handles sending SMS messages with specified phone numbers and message bodies. Operates on string-based parameters for recipients and content. Used to programmatically dispatch text messages from within an application.

Handles SMS sending with platform-specific configuration for Android, including intent setup and message formatting. Operates on custom types for Android options and general send options, enabling precise control over message delivery. Used to dispatch SMS messages with callback handlers for success and error states, tailored for mobile application integration.
